import React, { useEffect } from 'react' import "./about.css" import Aboutimg from "../../assets/aboutme.png"; const About = () => { useEffect(() => { const aboutContainer = document.querySelector('.about__container'); const aboutAnimatedElements = document.querySelectorAll('.about__animated'); const options = { root: null, rootMargin: '0px', threshold: 0.5, // Adjust this threshold as needed }; const handleIntersection = (entries, observer) => { entries.forEach((entry) => { if (entry.isIntersecting) { // Add the animation class to elements when they come into view aboutAnimatedElements.forEach((element) => { element.classList.add('fadeInUp'); }); // Disconnect the observer after the animation has been triggered observer.unobserve(aboutContainer); } }); }; const observer = new IntersectionObserver(handleIntersection, options); if (aboutContainer) { // Start observing the about section observer.observe(aboutContainer); } }, []); return (
